data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has been remarkably well-maintained and still gives that new home feel.  The open concept design features a large kitchen with a large island/breakfast bar, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances.  The living room is centrally located with a trayed ceiling and leads to the covered patio and the fully fenced back yard.  The primary suite offers a comfortably sized bedroom, a bath that includes a shower, separate double sinks, and a huge walk-in closet.  The utility room includes both gas and electric dryer connections and has plenty of room for storage.  All of this is located in the highly rated East Bernard school district.
